# Backend Environment Variables

## Overview
This template documents all environment variables needed for the backend service.
Copy to `.env` and fill in your values. **Never commit `.env` to git.**

## Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://promptledger:password@localhost:5432/promptledger_db
SQLALCHEMY_ECHO=false

## API Security
SECRET_KEY=your-secret-key-here-generate-with-openssl-rand-hex-32
JWT_EXPIRATION_HOURS=24

## Redis (Optional - for rate limiting and caching)
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379/0
ENABLE_REDIS_RATE_LIMITING=false  # Set to true if Redis is running

## Celery (Job Queue)
CELERY_BROKER_URL=redis://localhost:6379/1
CELERY_RESULT_BACKEND=redis://localhost:6379/2

## Observability & Monitoring
PROMETHEUS_ENABLED=true
ELASTICSEARCH_HOST=localhost
ELASTICSEARCH_PORT=9200
LOGSTASH_HOST=localhost
LOGSTASH_PORT=5000

## AWS S3 (File Uploads)
AWS_REGION=ap-southeast-1
AWS_S3_BUCKET=promptledger-uploads-dev-YOUR_ACCOUNT_ID
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your-aws-key-here
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your-aws-secret-here

## GitHub OAuth
GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=your-github-app-client-id
GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET=your-github-app-client-secret

## LLM Provider (OpenAI example)
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-key-here
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4

## Logging Level
LOG_LEVEL=INFO

## Additional Configuration
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:5173
API_PORT=8000
WORKERS=4
